Zero point energy                ...      0.29624476 Eh     185.90 kcal/mol
Thermal vibrational correction   ...      0.02058025 Eh      12.91 kcal/mol
Thermal rotational correction    ...      0.00141627 Eh       0.89 kcal/mol
